data.description: If you are looking for an affordable property in a great Rochester area you found it.  Ideal for buyer looking for a first home.  Spacious rooms, Brand New roof both house and garage, some newer windows, Central AC , full walk up attic and a two car garage perfect for cars, lawn equipment or extra storage. Oversized refinished back deck great for summer barbeques.  Hardwood floors and custom built-ins bring character and charm to the property. Cable and Greenlight internet ready for convenance and work from home.  Great location quiet safe neighborhood just minutes to stores, restaurants, and the quaint town of Webster.  East Irondequoit Schools.  Put your personal touches on the property and make it yours.
